headline.print_headline: Russian Military Action in Ukraine Would Be 'Grave Mistake': U.S
headline.main: Russian Military Action in Ukraine Would Be 'Grave Mistake': U.S

lead_paragraph: The United States warned Russia on Wednesday it would be a "grave mistake" to embark on a military intervention in Ukraine and said Washington was considering $1 billion in U.S. loan guarantees for Kiev.
